Text: Anybody want to seed this? This is the only one I got left on season 4. Pleeeeease?

Forget all these 'untouched' torrents. I have a super high speed connection and have been waiting for days for this idiot to emerge and seed. He's probably sitting there and grinning while the rest of us try to download a single byte.

Haha, yes, he managed to waste my time.
